==Italian==
===Etymology===
From Latin '''casa'''

===Pronunciation===
* IPA: /'kaza/

===Noun===
'''casa''' {{f}}, ''plural'' '''[[case]]'''

# [[house]]
# [[home]]
# [[shop]]
# (''boardgame'') [[square]]
# [[family]], [[dynasty]], [[descent]], [[extraction]], [[stock]], [[lineage]], [[birth]], [[origin]], [[race]] (not human 'race' (black, white, ...), but meaning the preceding words)
# [[company]], [[firm]]

