==Portuguese==
===Etymology===
From Latin '''casa'''

===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|pt-pt-casa.ogg|Audio (PT)}}

===Noun===
'''casa''' {{f}}, ''plural'' '''casas'''

#[[house]]

====Sayings====
'''Quem casa quer casa'''

#Those who marry want a house.

'''Casa roubada, trancas à porta'''

#Robbed house, locked doors.

